{"tid":2018890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國證實向世衛提外交照會 促邀請台灣參與WHA","createTime":"2020-05-16T01:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T08:15:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"484fddfeb48ad0ed707b8b82bc32ee143e3773ef","tid":2018890,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:55:12.000Z","msg":"德國證實向世衛提外交照會 促邀請台灣參與WHA<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202005160013.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202005160013.aspx&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b0967ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202005160013.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者林育立柏林15日專電）世衛大會即將登場，德國官員首度證實已向世界衛生組織（WHO）提出外交照會，並致函世衛秘書長譚德塞，支持台灣以觀察員身分參與大會。<br />\n<br />\n第73屆世界衛生大會（WHA）將在18日召開，德國外交部發言人柏格（Christofer Burger）今天表示，從2009年到2016年，德國即致力讓世衛邀請台灣以觀察員身分參加世衛大會，德國認為這樣的參與不需要以國家為前提。<br />\n<br />\n柏格指出，德國認為台灣的參與有助於對抗2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，俗稱武漢肺炎），因此7日與其他國家聯手向世衛秘書處提出外交照會，並與英國、法國、紐西蘭、美國、加拿大、澳洲等國聯名致函給世衛秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus），促邀請台灣以觀察員身分參加世衛大會。<br />\n<br />\n德國朝野議員也支持台灣重返世衛大會。世界報（Die Welt）報導，基民黨（CDU）籍的國會外交委員會主席洛特根（Norbert R&ouml;ttgen）表示，台灣曾長年以觀察員名義參加世衛大會，沒有理由不再發生。<br />\n<br />\n曾在去年訪台、同樣也是國會外交委員會成員的自民黨（FDP）議員雷赫特（Ulrich Lechte）指出，如果台灣是世衛大會觀察員，疫情可能就不會這麼嚴重，因為台灣去年底示警的電子郵件將有正式地位，世衛不能當作沒看到。"},{"pid":"0d11b9d25946faf935f0a8f6245fdf858f459af7","tid":2018890,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Send 左689抽水po 比德國未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b229273549bd66e3ee1cd1f098491083fe734112","tid":2018890,"uid":6058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0d11b9d25946faf935f0a8f6245fdf858f459af7","tid":2018890,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Send 左689抽水po 比德國未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P1zXQi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P1zXQi.png&h=9d93f96b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5942bef959e7940674a591a3c4bef55d5d98b86","tid":2018890,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話<br />\n德國收到由台灣捐來o既口罩後<br />\n官員唔敢講多謝，又取消接收儀式/記者會o既咩?"},{"pid":"49933508ca30b22bf1e398baa84eead0799dc8aa","tid":2018890,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"肯出聲既國家仲係太少"},{"pid":"83ff162c0c0e04f76a87abaf03f29988e8b6332a","tid":2018890,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"其實都係有啲難入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea2fdafd60c6f11e00b924f9f75009928136cdd","tid":2018890,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"末日國繼續縮龜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57f57a7a311a9068e3a82af9a31bfef8b874f0c","tid":2018890,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b229273549bd66e3ee1cd1f098491083fe734112","tid":2018890,"uid":6058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0d11b9d25946faf935f0a8f6245fdf858f459af7","tid":2018890,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Send 左689抽水po 比德國未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P1zXQi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P1zXQi.png&h=9d93f96b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src